page.title: 11FAMILY LIFE WARWICK BRIDGE
page.content: { }There are three{meals}a day breakfast,lunch and dinner. A common breakfast is toast and coffee and cereal. Most people go to Carlisle, but some go to Brampton for{shopping. The most comman{pets }are cats and dogs.They live in the house with the family. Mostly{mothers}keep the house tidy. {Fathers}are the main wage earners but many wives have parttime jobs.} Up to the age of eleven children go to local{Primary schools.}After that they mostly attend a{comprehensive {Secondary school}in Brampton. Some families share leisure interests and some have different hobbies.
